<p>3.1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;When registering as a User, the applicant must enter their e-mail address, select a password and submit other information requested by Tetenter and at the Portal Operator&#39;s discretion. Inter alia, Tetenter can prescribe requirements to the combination of letters and/or numbers forming a User ID and password and demand regular changing of the selected password due to security or other considerations.<br />
